    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and delivered to the tarmac via the M-variable differential lock. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; the double-VANOS system has been overhauled, and rod bearings were replaced to ensure peak reciprocating assembly health. The chassis remains rigid and communicative, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and poly-bushed trailing arms. This is a mechanically sorted, analog machine built for linear power delivery and exceptional lateral dynamics.",
